eaders for providing essential advice on how to tackle the management hurdles of a career sander also writes a monthly column for medical marketing  media sander’s latest book the best thing that could ever happen to you how a career reversal can reinvigorate your life big shoes publishing  was written to guide business professionals to reempower themselves after a job loss or get unstuck from a passionless career sander’s weekly radio show leader’s edge advances the ideas and debate of his leader’s edge blog selected in both  and  as the fordham business school’s commencement speaker sander has also been awarded the ohio state university’s professional achievement award and the osu pacesetter business leadership award sander received his undergraduate degree from the ohio state university followed by an mba degree from fairleigh dickinson university following his military career he went on to work for  years at lederle laboratories which merged into wyeth then pfizer in his tenure as marketing director of lederle rx products vaccines and oncology sander was responsible for many notable new product launches after lederle sander became chairman and ceo of euro rscg becker now havas life where he led a worldwide team of marketing strategists in introducing six blockbuster  billion healthcare brands in  medical advertising news named sander its man of the year and becker its agency of the year following becker sander went on to launch flaum navigators in  where he encourages and coaches his clients to embrace disruptive innovation in marketing sales and leadership contact sander today to learn how he can help your business amazoncom sander a flaum books biography blog audiobooks kindle amazoncom books interesting finds updated daily amazon try prime books all departments alexa skills amazon devices amazon video amazon warehouse deals appliances apps  games arts crafts  sewing automotive parts  accessories baby beauty  personal care books cds  vinyl cell phones  accesso