ful introduction of more than twenty widely used pharmaceutical productsadjunct professor of management science and executiveinresidence at the fordham university graduate school of business administration sander is a longtime champion of the big idea a business paradigm that creates and infuses breakthrough thinking up and down the marketing chain he is also founder and chair of the fordham leadership forum at fordham’s graduate school of business administration sander serves on the boards of the james cancer center the ohio state university fisher college of business the fordham university graduate school of business administration and eagle pharmaceuticals he is also a member of the nyc venture fellows program which is designed to mentor young entrepreneurssander received his undergraduate degree from the ohio state university followed by an mba degree magna cum laude from fairleigh dickinson university he worked eighteen years at lederle laboratories which merged into wyeth now a subsidiary of pfizer more recently sander was chairman of euro rscg life a worldwide network of fortythree healthcare agencies in  medical advertising news named sander its man of the year and the company he headed its agency of the year following his success at euro rscg life sander launched flaum navigators see more customers also bought items by scott w ventrella tom kelley spencer johnson are you an author help us improve our author pages by updating your bibliography and submitting a new or current image and biography › learn more at author central  paperback  kindle edition  paperback author updates blog post tired of being hammered for price gouging here’s some things we can do first we can get behind our industry’s “share the savings” initiative launched in early april   if you’re unfamiliar with the program here’s some background if you or someone in your family has had a medical procedure recently you’ve likely been astounded at the huge gap between listed charges and the disc